name: Dalihen
markerNotes: All releases date from 2025, with no prior history or presence. The Spotify bio raises suspicion of AI involvement, stating: "Every track is written from scars, heavy, melodic, unpolished, turned into noise through machines because the voice behind it couldn't stay quiet."
